org.afplib.afplib

Interface FND

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SF
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FNDImpl

    public interface FND
extends SF
    A representation of the model object 'FND'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Type Fc Desc
    • Ft Wt Class
    • Ft Wd Class
    • Max Pt Size
    • Nom Pt Size
    • Min Pt Size
    • Max HSize
    • Nom HSize
    • Min HSize
    • Dsn Gen Cls
    • Dsn Sub Cls
    • Dsn Spc Grp
    • Reserved1
    • Ft Ds Flags
    • Reserved2
    • GCSID
    • FGID
    • Triplets

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getFND()
